Automated Prediction Writeback

Use a special prediction field to save prediction scores directly on records.

Display Einstein Predictions Using Automated Prediction Writeback
Configure automated prediction writeback in Model Manager. Einstein scores newly created or updated records and writes the score to the prediction field.
Get Predictions With Bulk Scoring
Score predictions on multiple records at a time, including all records, a segment of the records, or records that have not reached the completed state.
